    <text>
    <body>
        <p>Originally organized as the 4th Kentucky Infantry on October 9, 1861, the unit was reorganized to the 4th Kentucky Mounted Infantry in the spring of 1864.  Mustered out August 17, 1865.</p>

    </body>
